OL,10,FThe number of living in poverty across
OL,11,Fthe UK has hit a record high, with
OL,12,Fcampaigners saying they are being
OL,13,Ffailed and forgotten.
OL,15,FThere were an estimated 4.33 million
OL,16,Fchildren in households in relative low
OL,17,Fincome after housing costs in the year
OL,18,Fto March 2023.
